[{"ave_id":"AVE-2000-0900","file_name":"2000/AVE-2000-0900.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2000-0348","title":"SCO UnixWare Sendmail 配置文件权限提升漏洞","description":"SCO UnixWare 7.1.0 及更早版本中 Sendmail 配置文件 sendmail.cf 存在权限配置缺陷，本地攻击者可利用该漏洞提升至 root 权限。由于 sendmail.cf 文件权限设置不当，攻击者能够修改配置文件或利用 Sendmail 的 setuid 机制执行恶意操作，从而完全控制目标系统。该漏洞影响 SCO UnixWare 7.1.0 及之前版本，CVSS 评分 10.0，危害等级严重。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-2000-0348"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"2001-03-12T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:51:31.803","remediation":"立即应用 SCO 安全公告 SB-99.10a 提供的补丁，修改 sendmail.cf 配置文件权限为 644 并移除 setuid 位。由于 SCO UnixWare 已停止维护，建议迁移至受支持的 Linux 或现代 Unix 系统，避免继续使用已不受支持的旧版本操作系统。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-20T00:00:00Z","references":["https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/4e8d44fc9434dcaf08511a3267e0bf049a6756de/cves/2000/0xxx/CVE-2000-0348.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-2000/CVE-2000-0348","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/470a5f1c0d1bd36cd0a6327cda49cf96a1474588/content/CVE-2000-0348.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/228df6a85079f5c6b1ecdfb3d41be685458438ef/CVE/data/2000/CVE-2000-0348.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/4544d3857250fe21711ce8febf38e8822729678f/advisories/unreviewed/2022/05/GHSA-62pv-x977-5p4f/GHSA-62pv-x977-5p4f.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x89000/88295/info.html","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/39f1db26eec9899ab2f8110ab3b45424c6fe9ec2/nvdcve/CVE-2000-0348.json","https://github.com/Yuning-J/VulnerabilityClassifier/blob/c0f06c21b73c26b5ee2b75c21a498eb04eada4b5/threatPrediction/cveIDThreatType/cve_idgainpre","https://github.com/nomi-sec/CVE-Easy-List/blob/dd9f81e9fd85457bf78c55783cb6a31e9af71d63/2000.tsv","https://github.com/hungryfoolou/Vulnerability_Mining/blob/3df1d8ed0489ae1228f975ae1f58a690aae53886/craw/