/security/advisories/NetBSD-SA1999-004.txt.asc 中的补丁。Linux 用户应更新 traceroute 包至最新版本，或限制本地用户对 traceroute 的 setuid 权限作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-20T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=91893782027835&w=2","http://www.osvdb.org/7574","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/712a40967986b700313860b08048435be4fa9839/cves/2000/0xxx/CVE-2000-0314.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-2000/CVE-2000-0314","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/1fe9b156eeeb72b8f8baa50bbe7bc0d9806e8c64/content/CVE-2000-0314.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/248c2167e720df96125f6ac9925793063a207510/CVE/data/2000/CVE-2000-0314.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/cdfc8886d71af7ef3bdab3e4db46753ff8af6538/advisories/unreviewed/2022/05/GHSA-c4h3-4hjj-m5cr/GHSA-c4h3-4hjj-m5cr.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x89000/88343/info.html","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_150600_150700.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/2000/CVE-2000-0314.json","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--ae4bac31-af94-4f46-9c2a-778b17bc2995.json","https://github.com/Vasileios-Mavroeidis/semantic-stix-vulnerability/blob/30f07606133364b9623f401bc306c8c9cbcf9386/vulnerability/vulnerability--ae4bac31-af94-4f46-9c2a-778b17bc2995.owl"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2000/AVE-2000-0313.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2000-0303","file_name":"2000/AVE-2000-0303.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2000-0312","title":"OpenBSD cron 本地权限提升漏洞","description":"OpenBSD 2.5 系统中的 cron 守护进程存在本地权限提升漏洞。当 cron 调用内部伪 popen 函数时，未能对 argv[] 参数数组进行正确的 NULL 终止处理，导致内存越界访问。具有本地访问权限的攻击者可利用特制参数触发此缺陷，从而获取 root 权限。该漏洞影响 OpenBSD 2.5 版本，需本地账户登录后方可利用。此漏洞由程序参数处理不当引起，CVSS 评分 7.2，危害等级高。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-2000-0312"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"2001-03-12T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:51:27.240","remediation":"升级至 OpenBSD 2.7 或更高版本（已修复 cron 中 argv 数组未正确 NULL 终止导致的权限提升漏洞），或应用 OpenBSD 官方安全补丁。临时缓解措施：限制本地用户 crontab 写入权限，移除不必要用户的 cron 访问能力。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-20T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.openbsd.org/errata25.html#cron","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/712a40967986b700313860b08048435be4fa9839/cves/2000/0xxx/CVE-2000-0312.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-2000/CVE-2000-0312","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/1fe9b156eeeb72b8f8baa50bbe7bc0d9806e8c64/content/CVE-2000-0312.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/248c2167e720df96125f6ac9925793063a207510/CVE/data/2000/CVE-2000-0312.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/cdfc8886d71af7ef3bdab3e4db46753ff8af6538/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-835h-phw4-qgfr/GHSA-835h-phw4-qgfr.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cwe_details/cwe_details_0_100.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x89000/88301/info.html","https://github.com/Team-Atlanta/aixcc-asc-atlantis/blob/785c446f980e12155935db586aa30c3b54adcc86/crs/src/crs-patch/smith/smith/lib/cwe/raw/CWE-170.txt","https://github.com/fkie-cad/nvd-json-data-feeds/blob/3508ccc52a2baed6a1946843005e8957c7067f39/CVE-2000/CVE-2000-03xx/CVE-2000-0312.json","https://github.com/ragiko/ntcir11/blob/e5b134c4e6784918dbfdc8a01d2c276d1847b032/workspace/gensim_sentence2vec/extract/36646.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/2000/POC-AVE-2000-0303.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2000/AVE-2000-0303.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2000-0298","file_name":"2000/AVE-2000-0298.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2000-0309","title":"OpenBSD DDB i386 trace-trap 处理本地拒绝服务漏洞","description":"OpenBSD 2.4 系统的 i386 架构跟踪陷阱处理函数中存在拒绝服务漏洞。当内核调试器（DDB）功能启用时，本地攻击者可通过触发特制的跟踪陷阱条件导致内核异常，进而造成系统崩溃或拒绝服务。该漏洞需要攻击者拥有本地用户权限且目标系统启用了 DDB 内核调试功能，攻击门槛较高，但成功利用后将严重影响系统可用性。","severity":"LOW","score":2.1,"aliases":["CVE-2000-0309"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"2001-03-12T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:51:26.870","remediation":"升级至 OpenBSD 2.5 或更高版本。若无法升级，从 OpenBSD 官方 errata 页面获取 patch 021 并应用到内核源码树后重新编译内核：`patch -p0 < 021_trctrap.patch`，然后 `cd /usr/src/sys/arch/i386/conf && config GENERIC && cd ../compile/GENERIC && make && make install` 并重启。如 DDB 非必需，临时缓解措施可在内核配置文件中移除 `options DDB` 后重新编译内核。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-20T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.openbsd.org/errata24.html#trctrap","http://www.osvdb.org/6126","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/e25ede9c3545efaa8ff0b393e30e48edb07502a8/cves/2000/0xxx/CVE-2000-0309.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-2000/CVE-2000-0309","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/1fe9b156eeeb72b8f8baa50bbe7bc0d9806e8c64/content/CVE-2000-0309.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/248c2167e720df96125f6ac9925793063a207510/CVE/data/2000/CVE-2000-0309.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/cdfc8886d71af7ef3bdab3e4db46753ff8af6538/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-cmfj-xq93-7whq/GHSA-cmfj-xq93-7whq.json","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/63d4031680b3d3fa77b826660a1e30ffc70ff5cd/nvdcve/CVE-2000-0309.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x89000/88324/info.html","https://github.com/hungryfoolou/Vulnerability_Mining/blob/3df1d8ed0489ae1228f975ae1f58a690aae53886/craw/cveid_craw/cveid_craw/data/cveid_by_kind/cveid_dos.txt","https://github.com/Vasileios-Mavroeidis/semantic-stix-vulnerability/blob/30f07606133364b9623f401bc306c8c9cbcf9386/vulnerability/vulnerability--b6f440bf-14a3-4986-a606-f51b5f75ec48.owl","https://github.com/williamjsmail/piranha/blob/e60f12e6edcde8585ee473f701c2421f6efe72d9/CVE2CAPEC/database/CVE-2000.jsonl"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2000/AVE-2000-0298.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2000-0297","file_name":"2000/AVE-2000-0297.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2000-0307","title":"SCO OpenServer xserver 端口资源拒绝服务漏洞","description":"SCO UnixWare 2.1.x 及 OpenServer 5.05 及更早版本中的 xserver 组件存在安全漏洞。本地攻击者可通过向 xserver 发送特制请求，导致系统拒绝服务，使得其他用户无法绑定 1024 以下的保留端口号。该漏洞影响 SCO UnixWare 2.1.x 和 OpenServer 5.05 及更早版本，CVSS 评分 5.0，危害等级中等。目前厂商已发布补丁修复此漏洞。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-2000-0307"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"2001-03-12T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:51:26.633","remediation":"建议升级 SCO OpenServer 至 5.06 及以上版本，或安装 SCO 官方提供的 xserver 安全补丁。临时缓解措施：限制本地用户对 X11 服务的访问权限，或在 xserver 配置中禁用低端口号绑定功能。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-20T00:00:00Z","references":["https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/e25ede9c3545efaa8ff0b393e30e48edb07502a8/cves/2000/0xxx/CVE-2000-0307.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-2000/CVE-2000-0307","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/1fe9b156eeeb72b8f8baa50bbe7bc0d9806e8c64/content/CVE-2000-0307.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/248c2167e720df96125f6ac9925793063a207510/CVE/data/2000/CVE-2000-0307.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/cdfc8886d71af7ef3bdab3e4db46753ff8af6538/advisories/unreviewed/2022/05/GHSA-ffrr-675f-6pxv/GHSA-ffrr-675f-6pxv.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x89000/88291/info.html","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/63d4031680b3d3fa77b826660a1e30ffc70ff5cd/nvdcve/CVE-2000-0307.json","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--53416e9c-1682-4fa9-b69f-2cb50fd99cfe.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/CVE-Easy-List/blob/0b7b3d855cd8fca7b800fb29d6754e2da82897b6/2000.tsv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2000/AVE-2000-0297.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2000-0264","file_name":"2000/AVE-2000-0264.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2000-0306","title":"SCO OpenServer calserver 远程缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"SCO OpenServer 系统中的 calserver 组件存在远程缓冲区溢出漏洞。未经身份认证的远程攻击者可通过向目标系统的 calserver 服务发送特制的超长消息，触发缓冲区溢出，从而以 root 权限执行任意代码。该漏洞影响 SCO OpenServer 5.0.x 版本，攻击无需任何认证即可远程利用，且漏洞利用代码已公开，实际危害较高。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-2000-0306"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"2001-03-12T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:51:26.513","remediation":"立即应用 SCO 安全公告 SB-99.02a 提供的补丁，升级 calserver 组件至修复版本。由于 SCO OpenServer 5 已停止维护，建议迁移至受支持的操作系统平台。临时缓解措施：在 inetd 配置中禁用 calserver 服务，或在防火墙层面限制对 calserver 端口（通常为 615/tcp）的访问。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-20T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/templates/archive.pike?list=1&date=1998-12-29&msg=AAh6GYsGU1%40leshka.chuvashia.su","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/20620","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/e25ede9c3545efaa8ff0b393e30e48edb07502a8/cves/2000/0xxx/CVE-2000-0306.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-2000/CVE-2000-0306","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/1fe9b156eeeb72b8f8baa50bbe7bc0d9806e8c64/content/CVE-2000-0306.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/248c2167e720df96125f6ac9925793063a207510/CVE/data/2000/CVE-2000-0306.json","https://github.com/eldondev/Snort/blob/34bdcf6a7a638b55c7c04f77ef1efa526ad08e33/doc/signatures/309.txt","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/cdfc8886d71af7ef3bdab3e4db46753ff8af6538/advisories/unreviewed/2022/05/GHSA-rx9m-8fvp-xhpf/GHSA-rx9m-8fvp-xhpf.json","https://github.com/rhuitl/uClinux/blob/0486e80a025dccbe4a2213715a2ab8a5063ea86b/user/snort/drop-rules/exploit.rules","https://github.com/bailehang/snort_2.2.0/blob/34f8a3a85f15645aea53d6e0d46863c7c57e43ef/doc/signatures/304.txt","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/2000/CVE-2000-0306.json","https://github.com/magicsword-io/Magic-SigExplorer/blob/2c28b91b003429a144a687199ee99ebd26f1a343/Magic-SigExplorer/docs/cve_report.md"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2000/AVE-2000-0264.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2000-0307","file_name":"2000/AVE-2000-0307.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2000-0313","title":"OpenBSD 2.6 本地接口媒体配置漏洞","description":"OpenBSD 2.6 存在权限控制缺陷，普通用户可修改系统网络接口的媒体配置参数（如速率、双工模式等），此操作本应仅限特权用户执行。攻击者利用该漏洞可篡改目标系统的网络接口配置，可能导致网络连接异常或拒绝服务。此漏洞影响所有硬件架构上的 OpenBSD 2.6 版本，CVSS 评分 4.6，危害等级中等。OpenBSD 官方已于 1999 年 11 月发布源代码补丁修复此问题。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":4.6,"aliases":["CVE-2000-0313"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"2001-03-12","updated":"2026-06-16T21:51:27.350","remediation":"立即应用 OpenBSD 官方补丁 002_ifmedia.patch（执行 cd /usr/src && patch -p0 < 002_ifmedia.patch），然后重新编译内核；或直接升级到 OpenBSD 2.7 及以上版本。如在生产环境，建议升级到仍在维护的最新 OpenBSD 稳定版以获全面安全更新。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-20T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.openbsd.org/errata.html#ifmedia","http://www.osvdb.org/7540","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/712a40967986b700313860b08048435be4fa9839/cves/2000/0xxx/CVE-2000-0313.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-2000/CVE-2000-0313","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/1fe9b156eeeb72b8f8baa50bbe7bc0d9806e8c64/content/CVE-2000-0313.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/248c2167e720df96125f6ac9925793063a207510/CVE/data/2000/CVE-2000-0313.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/cdfc8886d71af7ef3bdab3e4db46753ff8af6538/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-84m3-hwqx-qqwm/GHSA-84m3-hwqx-qqwm.json","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/63d4031680b3d3fa77b826660a1e30ffc70ff5cd/nvdcve/CVE-2000-0313.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_150600_150700.json","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--23b012c2-b67b-4bcc-9726-63a0784bfb73.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/CVE-Easy-List/blob/0b7b3d855cd8fca7b800fb29d6754e2da82897b6/2000.tsv","https://github.com/Vasileios-Mavroeidis/semantic-stix-vulnerability/blob/30f07606133364b9623f401bc306c8c9cbcf9386/vulnerability/vulnerability--23b012c2-b67b-4bcc-9726-63a0784bfb73.owl"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2000/AVE-2000-0307.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2000-0002","file_name":"2000/AVE-2000-0002.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2000-0760","title":"Apache Tomcat Snoop Servlet 信息泄露漏洞","description":"Jakarta Tomcat 3.0 和 3.1 版本中的 Snoop Servlet 存在信息泄露漏洞。远程攻击者无需认证即可向目标服务器发送一个不存在的 .snp 后缀 URL 请求，触发 Snoop Servlet 返回系统属性、环境变量、请求参数等敏感信息。该漏洞可能导致服务器内部配置和文件路径等关键信息暴露，为攻击者后续入侵提供情报基础，影响所有运行在 Apache 下的 Tomcat 3.0 及 3.1 版本。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":6.4,"aliases":["CVE-2000-0760"],"sources":["nuclei"],"published":"2000-10-20T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:52:25.440","remediation":"升级到 Tomcat 3.2 或更高版本以彻底移除 Snoop Servlet；若无法升级，删除 `$CATALINA_HOME/webapps/ROOT/WEB-INF/web.xml` 中 Snoop Servlet 的 `<servlet-mapping>` 配置，或直接移除 `snoop.jar` 文件，并重启 Tomcat 服务使配置生效。也可在 Apache 反向代理层添加访问规则，拦截对 `*.snp` 路径的请求作为临时缓解。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-15T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/1532","http://www.securityfocus.com/frames/?content=/templates/archive.pike%3Flist%3D1%26date%3D2000-07-15%26msg%3DPine.SUN.3.96.1000719235404.24004A-100000%40grex.cyberspace.org","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/20132","https://github.com/projectdiscovery/nuclei-templates/blob/main/http/cves/2000/CVE-2000-0760.yaml","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/a90de4f84b4783951362f491671e1e9decfc17cb/2000/CVE-2000-0760.md","https://github.com/projectdiscovery/nuclei-templates/blob/a5c2e8e4dab8c8e618ba76807c3e07587b7d781a/http/cves/2000/CVE-2000-0760.yaml","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/d5838f491a2d04e9f823fb9638e9e6f0b038d399/cves/2000/0xxx/CVE-2000-0760.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-2000/CVE-2000-0760","https://github.com/ARPSyndicate/suricata-vedas/blob/fe24794ad36564b5bbc7c69101525011387b8650/2000/CVE-2000-0760.rules","https://github.com/hack007x/veil_poc/blob/5cfe1da6e975ba816d728597885a5c5e79bda8bd/cves/2000/CVE-2000-0760.poc","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/a7dc09e86ccf6c48996b8c45fb9dcbb33ad05167/CVE/data/2000/CVE-2000-0760.json","https://github.com/p0dalirius/ApacheTomcatScanner/blob/af5077ce3aeae4c7df3be909998bb54e3812c742/apachetomcatscanner/data/vulnerabilities/2000/CVE-2000-0760.json","https://github.com/InfoSecWarrior/Vulnerable-Box-Resources/blob/c784bcf63e1ec5c3a0116043d8653d00f0a21a0b/Infosecwarrior/My-Tomcat-Host/MyTomcatHost-1-nuclei-8080-output.txt","https://github.com/runZeroInc/nuclei-templates/blob/89af8e391d368228625addfe3ecc6aee3b5d0345/http/cves/2000/CVE-2000-0760.yaml"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/2000/POC-AVE-2000-0002.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2000/AVE-2000-0002.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2000-0363","file_name":"2000/AVE-2000-0363.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2000-0354","title":"GNU Mirror 2.8.x 目录遍历漏洞","description":"Linux 系统中 mirror 2.8.x 版本存在路径遍历漏洞，远程攻击者可通过在镜像同步过程中构造特制的目录遍历路径，将文件写入到本地目标目录的上一级目录中，实现越目录文件创建。该漏洞源于 mirror 工具对目标路径的规范化处理不充分，未有效过滤 `../` 等相对路径序列，导致攻击者可在目标系统上任意位置创建文件，进而可能结合其他漏洞实现权限提升或代码执行。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-2000-0354"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"2000-09-28","updated":"2026-06-16","remediation":"升级 GNU Mirror 至 2.9 及以上版本（最后一个版本为 2.9），该版本修复了目录遍历问题。由于 Mirror 已停止维护，建议迁移至 rsync 或 wget 等活跃维护的替代工具；若必须继续使用旧版本，应在配置文件中对目标路径参数进行严格校验，阻止包含 ../ 的路径。同时以最小权限运行 Mirror 进程，限制其写入目录范围。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-20T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.debian.org/security/1999/19991018","http://www.novell.com/linux/security/advisories/suse_security_announce_22.html","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/681","http://www.securityfocus.com/templates/archive.pike?list=1&msg=15769.990928%40tomcat.ru"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2000/AVE-2000-0363.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2000-0247","file_name":"2000/AVE-2000-0247.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2000-0278","title":"SalesLogix eViewer slxweb.dll 未授权访问拒绝服务漏洞","description":"SalesLogix eViewer 的 slxweb.dll 管理程序未对用户进行身份认证，远程攻击者可通过直接访问该组件的 URL 发送管理命令（如 command=shutdown）导致进程终止。由于该组件默认安装在 Web 服务器的 /scripts 目录且无法更改位置，攻击者可重复发送请求造成持续性拒绝服务，使应用程序无法正常提供服务。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-2000-0278"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"2000-08-03T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:51:22.993","remediation":"从 Web 服务器中移除 slxweb.dll 管理组件，或在 Web 服务器配置中限制对 /scripts/slxweb.dll 及 /scripts/slxweb.dll/admin 的访问路径，仅允许受信任的内网地址访问并启用身份认证。如短期内无法移除，应在边界防火墙或反向代理上阻断外部对 slxweb.dll 管理接口的未授权请求。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-19T00:00:00Z","references":["http://archives.neohapsis.com/archives/bugtraq/current/0006.html","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/1089","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19835","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/dde4d96d7c1eff197b9a15817af615500736afa7/cves/2000/0xxx/CVE-2000-0278.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-2000/CVE-2000-0278","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/1fe9b156eeeb72b8f8baa50bbe7bc0d9806e8c64/content/CVE-2000-0278.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/666a3c9c944f5ed9f7d7ff0aa29b047387ce02f3/CVE/data/2000/CVE-2000-0278.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/ce77465efdf58fc31a7a0bc8c83705be48abcedf/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-9v3f-j9v9-gvh5/GHSA-9v3f-j9v9-gvh5.json","https://github.com/Freem93/grammar_nasl_v2/blob/63834ebb8cd6e97050e155291c7500ad53bb20c6/plugins/eviewer.nasl","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/2000/CVE-2000-0278.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_152600_152700.json","https://github.com/andreafioraldi/ToolsForCyberChallenge/blob/197d3dfd204cf1b9d1af1451455c8831c3ff9948/generated/files_5.list.dict","https://github.com/hungryfoolou/Vulnerability_Mining/blob/3df1d8ed0489ae1228f975ae1f58a690aae53886/craw/cveid_craw/cveid_craw/data/cveid_by_kind/cveid_dos.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":["https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19835"],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/2000/POC-AVE-2000-0247.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/exploits/2000/EXP-AVE-2000-0247.toml"],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":true,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2000/AVE-2000-0247.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2000-0310","file_name":"2000/AVE-2000-0310.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2000-0377","title":"Microsoft Windows NT 4.0 Remote Registry 拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Windows NT 4.0 远程注册表服务存在认证缺陷漏洞，本地认证用户可通过向目标系统发送特制的畸形请求，导致 winlogon 进程异常崩溃，从而引发拒绝服务。该漏洞影响 Windows NT 4.0 系统，攻击者需拥有本地合法账户权限，无法远程匿名利用。Microsoft 已在安全公告 MS00-040 中提供安全更新修复此漏洞。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-2000-0377"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"2000-06-08T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:51:35.390","remediation":"安装 Microsoft 安全公告 MS00-040 对应补丁 (Q259728) 修复 Remote Registry 服务认证绕过缺陷。临时缓解措施：禁用 Remote Registry 服务或将注册表远程访问权限限定于指定管理员组。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-20T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.microsoft.com/technet/support/kb.asp?ID=264684","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/1331","https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/security-updates/securitybulletins/2000/ms00-040","https://oval.cisecurity.org/repository/search/definition/oval%3Aorg.mitre.oval%3Adef%3A1021","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/20006","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/712a40967986b700313860b08048435be4fa9839/cves/2000/0xxx/CVE-2000-0377.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-2000/CVE-2000-0377","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/1fe9b156eeeb72b8f8baa50bbe7bc0d9806e8c64/content/CVE-2000-0377.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/248c2167e720df96125f6ac9925793063a207510/CVE/data/2000/CVE-2000-0377.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/cdfc8886d71af7ef3bdab3e4db46753ff8af6538/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-x6w9-h4wh-qw7r/GHSA-x6w9-h4wh-qw7r.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/2000/CVE-2000-0377.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_detai